 and frank evaluation to take place and, for this </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">reason, I am unable to provide you with the risk register at this stage. My officials will </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.25pt">obviously be able to talk to you about the high level risks that they are managing and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:12pt">mitigating against, but they will not share detail on the risk register itself with the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">Committee.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 152.15pt 7.2pt 169.2pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:88%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:88%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:88%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">November 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>